<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Profil NOC Engineer</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; background-color: #1a1a1a; color: #00ff00; padding: 50px; }
        .container { border: 1px solid #00ff00; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; }
        h1 { border-bottom: 2px solid #00ff00; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        .status { background-color: #333; padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 5px; color: #fff; }
        ul { list-style-type: "> "; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Hello World!</h1>
        <p>Status: <span class="status">System Online</span></p>
        <p>Saya adalah seorang <strong>NOC Engineer</strong> yang fokus pada infrastruktur jaringan dan optimasi sistem.</p>
        
        <h3>Keahlian & Minat:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Network Administration (Cisco & GNS3)</li>
            <li>Linux Server Management (Ubuntu)</li>
            <li>Version Control (Git & GitHub)</li>
            <li>Hardware Optimization</li>
        </ul>

        <p><em>"Monitoring traffic, solving issues, and keeping the world connected."</em></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
